{"tid":2136623,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 摺被駐港部隊high撚到  take咗啲強國種子嚟？","createTime":"2020-08-02T09:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T04:26:29.000Z","uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2afb7249bebb14a01ce3312cc643f7e394f034a9","tid":2136623,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"港毒之父傷心過度，代佢出微博post一天<br />\n<br />\n驻香港部队 <br />\n今天 13:00 来自 微博 <a href=\"http://weibo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e86ddb60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">weibo.com</a><br />\n#致敬人民子弟兵# #唱战歌颂英雄# 【我是子弹】日前，驻香港部队文工队走进各个营区，为基层官兵们带去&ldquo;八一&rdquo;建军节的祝福。《我是子弹》这首歌曲展现了中国军人的阳刚之气，也表明了官兵们时刻准备着的决心与信心。@广西武警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4979741/org/6cc76240995c7a45775ee6321d1e8e39.jpg/IZAFGS5MRxbQXdhDeE2mVv-WMUK_GoUkJepzZCXqc2Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4979741%2Forg%2F6cc76240995c7a45775ee6321d1e8e39.jpg%2FIZAFGS5MRxbQXdhDeE2mVv-WMUK_GoUkJepzZCXqc2Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2f925640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4979742/org/27a5bd00f1dc7a2ecb48a803c7faa511.jpg/rfSaF0CIYIqupYAMhpBrQXoN7A7yxJZmMXDvxDFw78Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4979742%2Forg%2F27a5bd00f1dc7a2ecb48a803c7faa511.jpg%2FrfSaF0CIYIqupYAMhpBrQXoN7A7yxJZmMXDvxDFw78Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b0cb3d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4979740/org/88d7def141bb7462a538a58f420a382f.jpg/jz4RhNAcCqKmupOjpVzpEZmsXlwEt38zbJvxQ2yb8UM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4979740%2Forg%2F88d7def141bb7462a538a58f420a382f.jpg%2Fjz4RhNAcCqKmupOjpVzpEZmsXlwEt38zbJvxQ2yb8UM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=bc36262e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我是子弹 出膛看谁敢嚣张<img sr