T09:49:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">女子仪仗排每人每年流的汗水近0.5吨，至少穿破3双马靴</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，阅兵场上短短2分钟的亮相，至少需要付出150多个日日夜夜的训练，服役2年，踢出正步距离达2000多公里，差不多是从香港到北京的距离。<br />\n<br />\n驻香港部队三军仪仗队女子仪仗排，被誉为&ldquo;香江紫荆、铿锵玫瑰&rdquo;，荣立集体三等功1次。组建以来，<span class=\"red\">先后参加香港青少年军事夏令营、香港大学生军事体验营、庆祝香港回归20周年阅兵、&ldquo;七一&rdquo;军营开放、中秋探访、军民联谊等重大活动</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，作风纪律严、标准要求高，完成任务圆满出色，展示了威武文明、爱港亲民的良好形象。<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.ws.126.net/2020/0731/c4226405p00qec0re00vbd200qo00hsg00id00c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0731%2Fc4226405p00qec0re00vbd200qo00hsg00id00c8.png&h=1d44adc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.ws.126.net/2020/0731/68568e91p00qec0rf00rxd200qo00hqg00id00c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0731%2F68568e91p00qec0rf00rxd200qo00hqg00id00c7.png&h=196282f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7460a1050f65ef931d8912c23f68315a644dfe22","tid":2136623,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"港父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca258ce7b09215adb8a354a3331076bc22cf2d2","tid":2136623,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46040d49bfd5920579f7cf06ed0a6d9962ef5989","tid":2136623,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59e476bdde60604a8b8ddb5e65c143c510a37264","tid":2136623,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"#驻港仪仗女兵版无价之姐# 【驻香港部队女兵飒不飒】有这样一群笑靥如花的阳光女孩，她们齐聚东方之珠，梦想起航、乘风破浪，她们&ldquo;不爱红装爱武装&rdquo;，她们&ldquo;起步就震撼，亮相就精彩&rdquo;，她们就是英姿飒爽的驻香港部队三军仪仗队女子仪仗排。一起去看看她们的华丽变身吧！<br />\n<img src=