humbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.i21st.cn%2Fuploads%2Farticle%2Fspeaking%2F21%2FIMG_63082%2F1.thumb.gif&h=56c51286&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"原來有班咁既支那閪係香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:48:34.000Z","msg":"慰安婦黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"王轩 从空乘到仪仗兵<br />\n  &ldquo;入伍前我是空中乘务与模特专业，从台步到正步、从空乘到仪仗兵，对于自己的选择并不后悔，我要一直努力下去。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.ws.126.net/2020/0731/0cf7066cp00qec0r800rnd200u000k0g00id00c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0731%2F0cf7066cp00qec0r800rnd200u000k0g00id00c8.png&h=e5b369dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n达瓦卓玛 从坚毅的藏族姑娘到仪仗兵<br />\n  &ldquo;指尖滴下的汗水和弥漫的汗味是对青春奋斗最好的诠释，我要更努力地奋斗下去，让自己的青春不留遗憾。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.ws.126.net/2020/0731/b2d753ccp00qec0r900m2d200u000k0g00id00c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0731%2Fb2d753ccp00qec0r900m2d200u000k0g00id00c8.png&h=575abc52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尤乔冉 从大学新生到仪仗兵<br />\n  &ldquo;能成为一名驻香港部队仪仗兵，是我在最美的青春里做出的最光荣的选择。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.ws.126.net/2020/0731/8ff8ebfcp00qec0r900mgd200u000k0g00id00c8.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=png&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0731%2F8ff8ebfcp00qec0r900mgd200u000k0g00id00c8.png%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Dpng%26interlace%3D1&h=a4de3c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郭小丽 从上海交通大学在读生到仪仗兵<br />\n  &ldquo;从天之骄子到军中绿花，坚强、自律、拼搏，我在这里遇到了更好的自己，变成了自己喜欢的样子。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.ws.126.net/2020/0731/19ec04a8p00qec0ra00r4d200u000k0g00id00c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0731%2F19ec04a8p00qec0ra00r4d200u000k0g00id00c8.png&h=6c826162&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39cb571b99f01e4e4c6c770bdc8e6a158dc4664d","tid":213662